column4: NSLOCTEXT("[A6097D4E40A168EFEEC3F8A42CB6780A]", "B2EB325C418CD740F20D2184A64FF8C1", "Hey, you\'ve been in these bug battle contests, right?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A6097D4E40A168EFEEC3F8A42CB6780A]", "DECC74434372B83CB2FF49910C5473B3", "Do you know where Tentomon sleeps? In Native Forest?")
NSLOCTEXT("[A6097D4E40A168EFEEC3F8A42CB6780A]", "838DF57144184BE9D4329CB3360C628B", "Baby Digimons sleep there. When they wake up, they become Tentomon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[A6097D4E40A168EFEEC3F8A42CB6780A]", "15B64EE549EC567F8737FAB3CC33BBBC", "But, sometimes they don\'t. It\'s a matter of luck.")
